paragraphs.title: load raw data
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyspark.sql import Row
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf

pmdata = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///pm/airkorea/pm_final.parquet')
# 이상 값 제거
pmdata.show()
pmdata.printSchema()

paragraphs.title: geocode api test (API 호출횟수 제한 주의!!)
mapping latlon on address dict (API호출횟수 제한 주의!)
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyjake.geo.api_kakao_geocode import getLatLon
from pyspark.sql.types import StructType, StructField, StringType, DoubleType
import pandas as pd

dataset_rows = []

for stcode in dict_addr.keys():
    location = str(dict_loc[int(stcode)])
    address = str(dict_addr[int(stcode)])
    lat, lon = getLatLon(address)
    row = [location, stcode, address, float(lat), float(lon)]
    dataset_rows.append(row)
    print(row)

# make pdf
pdf = pd.DataFrame(dataset_rows, columns=('location', 'station_code', 'address', 'lat', 'lon'))

# make spdf
schema = StructType([
    StructField('location', StringType()),
    StructField('station_code', StringType()),
    StructField('address', StringType()),
    StructField('lat', DoubleType()),
    StructField('lon', DoubleType())
])
spdf = spark.createDataFrame(pdf, schema)

# save spdf
spdf.write.mode('overwrite').parquet('hdfs:///pm/airkorea/pm_location.parquet')

print('위경도 가져오기 완료!')
print(pdf)

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import IntegerType

udf_dh2m = udf(lambda s: int(s.split('-')[1]), IntegerType())

pmdata_latlon = pmdata_latlon.withColumn('month', udf_dh2m('datetime'))
pmdata_latlon.createOrReplaceTempView('pmdata_latlon')

%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import IntegerType
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_floatize, udf_intize

udf_dh2m = udf(lambda s: int(s.split('-')[1]), IntegerType())
udf_int = udf(lambda s: int(s), IntegerType())

monthly_pm = pmdata_latlon.withColumn('month', udf_dh2m('datetime'))\
                            .drop('datetime')\
                            .withColumn('pm10', udf_int('pm10'))\
                            .withColumn('pm25', udf_int('pm25'))\
                            .groupby('station_code', 'month', 'lat', 'lon')\
                            .sum('pm10', 'pm25')\
                            .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10)', 'pm10')\
                            .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25)', 'pm25')\
                            .withColumn('lat', udf_floatize('lat'))\
                            .withColumn('lon', udf_floatize('lon'))

monthly_pm.show()

paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyspark.sql import Row

def getMonth(s):
    if s == 'Jan':
        return 1
    elif s == 'Feb':
        return 2
    elif s == 'Mar':
        return 3
    elif s == 'Apr':
        return 4
    elif s == 'May':
        return 5
    elif s == 'Jun':
        return 6
    elif s == 'Jul':
        return 7
    elif s == 'Aug':
        return 8
    elif s == 'Sep':
        return 9
    elif s == 'Oct':
        return 10
    elif s == 'Nov':
        return 11
    elif s == 'Dec':
        return 12

udf_ym2m = udf(lambda s: getMonth(s.split('-')[0]), IntegerType())

weather = sc.textFile('hdfs:///raw/monthly-weather.csv')\
            .map(lambda s: s.split(','))
aws_location = sc.textFile('hdfs:///raw/aws_location.csv')\
                .map(lambda s: s.split(','))
header = weather.first()
header2 = aws_location.first()

mw = weather.filter(lambda s: s != header)\
            .map(lambda s: Row(aws_station_code=s[0], ym=s[1], avg_windv=s[9], max_windv=s[10], max_windd=s[11]))\
            .toDF()\
            .withColumn('month', udf_ym2m('ym'))
            
aws_l = aws_location.filter(lambda s: s != header2)\
                    .map(lambda s: Row(aws_station_code=s[0], aws_lat=s[1], aws_lon=s[2]))\
                    .toDF()

mw.join(aws_l, 'aws_station_code').show()
# mw.show()
# aws_l.show()
aws_l.createOrReplaceTempView('aws_location')
